Finally, as a finishing touch, add charcoal and chili pepper as a deodorizer, and add Natsume. This will conclude Jean's marination.

43
00:09:44,351 --> 00:10:04,351
From now until spring, we will continue to watch over Jean's maturation.

44
00:10:04,351 --> 00:10:24,351
In early spring, remove the lid of Jean's jar, and in the evening, put the lid back on. By releasing the gas produced during fermentation, the activity of the bacteria becomes more vigorous, resulting in a rich Jean.

45
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:45,920
The wisdom of fermenting soybeans to make seasoning was born in China.

46
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:53,920
This is the oldest Chinese dictionary, "Questions and Answers," which was compiled in China 1,800 years ago.

47
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:58,920
In this, a food called "Thread" appears.

48
00:10:58,920 --> 00:11:06,920
This "Thread" is made by adding salt and fermenting beans.

49
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:10,920
To "ferment" means to "cultivate."

50
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:25,920
A rich country-style "Sichuan Xiao" opened in the middle of Yo-sko.

51
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:33,920
Sichuan cuisine in this area is known for its use of various seasonings and has become a representative cuisine of China.

52
00:11:47,711 --> 00:11:57,312
I looked at the Jean sales area in the town market. In China, they also call the soy sauce and miso family "Jean."

53
00:11:57,312 --> 00:12:07,312
In front of the store, along with miso containing soy sauce and chili pepper, there was a seasoning called "Tangi" being sold.

54
00:12:07,312 --> 00:12:31,312
The best-selling seasoning in the Jean sales area is this chili pepper. In fact, this is a poem written in ancient books over 1,800 years ago.

55
00:12:31,312 --> 00:12:59,312
Uncle, who came to sell chili peppers in the town. He says that these chili peppers are homemade. Boil soybeans, inoculate with natural bacteria, ferment, and add salt. All the farmers say they make chili peppers.

56
00:12:59,312 --> 00:13:19,312
Chili peppers have survived for over 2,000 years, crossing time and continuing to live in the warm gaze of people. I visited farmers in the outskirts of the city to see how they are used now.

57
00:13:19,312 --> 00:13:42,312
They say that chili peppers are an essential seasoning ingredient for stir-fries. First, finely chop the chili peppers and stir-fry them in oil. Then, use the dissolved parts in the oil to season the dish.

58
00:13:42,312 --> 00:13:51,312
这种从黑油中飘出来的香味，跟炒日本酱油的时候完全一样。

59
